dct_description_sm: Map shows Santiago de Cuba city center with inset diagrams of progress of November 30 revolutionary uprising. On verso: map of voyage of the Granma from Mexico to Cuba, map of movements of revolutionary uprising after disembarcation, and written history of Cuban Revolution.
dct_creator_sm: Cuba. Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, issuing body
dct_publisher_sm: Habana, Cuba : Instituto Cubano de Geodesia y Cartografía, 1976.
